WEBVTT

00:11.745 --> 00:13.656
- <i>Something in life,
you're always Worried</i>

00:13.680 --> 00:16.286
<i>about car bombs, shootings.</i>

00:16.315 --> 00:19.263
<i>- This is the most resilient
community in the world.</i>

00:19.285 --> 00:22.129
<i>People survive.
People don't break down.</i>

00:22.155 --> 00:24.362
<i>People are exposed
to awful things here.</i>

00:24.391 --> 00:26.029
<i>- You walk around the corner</i>

00:26.059 --> 00:28.266
<i>and possibly</i> a <i>bomb will go off
or</i> a <i>shooting.</i>

00:28.294 --> 00:29.602
<i>It's just part of life, really.</i>

00:29.629 --> 00:31.438
- <i>There's no point
in being bitter.</i>

00:31.464 --> 00:34.240
<i>All it does in the end
is intensify the situation,</i>

00:34.267 --> 00:36.304
<i>and it widens the whole wound
in Northern Ireland.</i>

00:36.336 --> 00:37.542
<i>- We actually are surviving.</i>

00:37.570 --> 00:39.345
<i>That's the whole story
of Belfast.</i>

00:39.372 --> 00:41.113
<i>- It's really only</i>
a <i>tit-for-tat thing.</i>

00:41.141 --> 00:42.518
<i>Kill</i> a <i>Catholic,
kill</i> a <i>Protestant,</i>

