- You got him
a leather photo album.

02:47.767 --> 02:49.747
- Couldn't we do better
than that?

02:49.769 --> 02:50.770
What are the Irish getting him?

02:50.803 --> 02:53.647
- Well, Bertie's got him a bowl
carved from a tree

