- <i>I asked her
three or four times...</i>

07:00.119 --> 07:02.429
- <i>She assured</i> me
<i>she was all right.</i>

07:02.455 --> 07:03.729
<i>She screamed every time.</i>

07:05.658 --> 07:07.069
<i>The fifth time I asked her,</i>

07:07.093 --> 07:09.505
<i>she said,
"Daddy, I love you very much."</i>

07:11.531 --> 07:12.942
<i>That's what her last words were.</i>

